sequenceDiagram
    actor H as Human
    participant D as /deploy
    participant Cfg as Company Config
    participant Stg as Staging
    participant Prd as Production
    participant FS as docs/releases/

    H->>D: /deploy

    note over D: Pre-flight
    D->>D: Read .claude/deploy.md (staging, production, health check, rollback)
    D->>Cfg: Cross-check deployment_chain + deployment_manual_gates
    alt deploy.md missing
        D->>H: ⛔ No deploy config — create .claude/deploy.md first
    end
    alt No rollback command configured
        D->>H: ⚠️ No rollback — type PROCEED to continue without it
        H->>D: PROCEED
    end

    D->>FS: Read PI-N-RN-gono.md — verify GO decision
    alt No Go/No Go record
        D->>H: ⛔ Run /go-nogo first — mandatory gate
    else Decision is NO-GO
        D->>H: ⛔ Go/No Go was NO-GO — deployment blocked
    end

    D->>H: Present deployment plan (version, environments, health check)
    H->>D: CONFIRM

    note over D: Stage 1 — Staging (if configured)
    D->>Stg: Run staging deployment command
    D->>Stg: Run health check
    alt Health check fails
        D->>H: ❌ Staging failed — ROLLBACK / INVESTIGATE / STOP
        H->>D: Decision
    end
    D->>H: ✅ Staging OK — type PROMOTE to deploy to production
    H->>D: PROMOTE

    alt Manual gate before production (deployment_manual_gates)
        D->>H: ✋ Manual gate: [gate name] — confirm before proceeding
        H->>D: Confirmed
    end

    note over D: Stage 2 — Production
    D->>Prd: Run production deployment command
    D->>Prd: Run health check
    alt Health check fails
        D->>H: ❌ Production failed — ROLLBACK / INVESTIGATE / STOP
        H->>D: Decision
        alt ROLLBACK
            D->>Prd: Run rollback command
            D->>Prd: Verify health check
        end
    end

    D->>FS: Append to docs/releases/deploy-log.md
    D->>D: Update idea diagram → diagram-v5-deployed.mmd
    D->>H: ✅ Deployment complete — suggest /pir [PROJ-NNN]
